            "type": "note",
            "content": "✔ **SUMMARY SHORT NOTES**<br/>• Subject → I, we, you, he, she, it, they<br/>• Object → me, us, you, him, her, it, them<br/>• Possessive Adj → my, our, your, his, her, its, their<br/>• Possessive Pronoun → mine, ours, yours, his, hers, theirs<br/>• Reflexive → myself, yourself, himself…<br/>• Order → 2 → 3 → 1<br/>• Preposition के बाद object<br/>• Comparison → than + (I/me)"
